{"tid":1269991,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"不開心就不開心 也別勉強的慰問","createTime":"2019-06-30T17:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T18:44:32.000Z","uid":191453,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6c2e5cb22252a5a1395947ef5e0291674db700","tid":1269991,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:30:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oEE0JaT-QVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoEE0JaT-QVs&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=c9e3b1a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oEE0JaT-QVs</a><br />\n開不了心 <br />\n主唱: 陳奕迅<br />\n曲: 伍卓賢 <br />\n詞: 林夕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一想起我們有話要講 未曾被聽見便閉幕<br />\n猶幸我愛惜這個地方 仍然盛放</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不開心就不開心 也別勉強的慰問<br />\n但求隨著我的心 灑脫地尊重我的傷感<br />\n別要 不開心便找開心 去避過我的良心<br />\n消化憂鬱後 才令我拾回自信心<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一個都嫌多🕯一個都不能少</strong>"},{"pid":"5988db9f2959b7f77692d62fbb285c4c6a08dc51","tid":1269991,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yKjDHw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yKjDHw.png&h=e15286a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b06a42b132d522f0f070d085960986d268954a5","tid":1269991,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:54:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>多一個人走出嚟 多一分力量</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyy8wqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdyy8wqz.jpg&h=18391795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b14770d7066c5583685fa45700408ee4911f999","tid":1269991,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yDWFn9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyDWFn9b.png&h=b8428e5d&s={S